content_generation.xlsx_generation:
Create contents for an Excel spreadsheet. Return a JSON object with the following structure:
{
  "sheets": [
    {
      "name": "SheetName",
      "headers": ["Header1", "Header2", ...],
      "data": [
        ["Row1Cell1", "Row1Cell2", ...],
        ["Row2Cell1", "Row2Cell2", ...]
      ]
    }
  ]
}

